Liverpool legend, Jamie Carragher, has predicted who will win the Champions League this season. While the chances of holders Chelsea to make it to the semifinals of this competition are very slim after their 3-1 home loss to Real Madrid on Wednesday night, Liverpool and Manchester City are better placed to move to the next round. Liverpool defeated Benfica 3-1 in Portugal while Manchester City worked hard to beat Atletico Madrid 1-0 at the Etihad. Bayern Munich suffered a 1-0 loss to Spanish side Villarreal Carragher predicted the outcome of this season’s clashes from the quarter-finals to the final match. UCL predictions: Quarter-finals Chelsea vs Real Madrid – CHELSEA Manchester City vs Atletico Madrid – MANCHESTER CITY Bayern Munich vs Villarreal – BAYERN MUNICH Benfica vs Liverpool – LIVERPOOL Semi-finals Chelsea vs Manchester City – MANCHESTER CITY Bayern Munich vs Liverpool – LIVERPOOL Final Manchester City vs Liverpool – LIVERPOOL.